# =============================================================================
# Netlify / Cloudflare Pages Redirects
# =============================================================================
# Covers WordPress migration + category/tag consolidation (March 2026).
# Rules are processed top-to-bottom; first match wins.
# Without the ! (force) suffix, redirects only fire when no file exists at the
# requested path — so existing static pages (e.g. /accessibility/) are safe.
#
# IMPORTANT: Cloudflare Pages limits dynamic rules (with * or :splat) to 100.
# Static rules that appear AFTER a dynamic rule count as dynamic.
# Therefore, ALL static (exact-match) rules MUST come before ANY dynamic rules.
# =============================================================================


